Every Wufoo user gets access to...
----------------------------------

Here’s just some of the features you get with all of our Wufoo plans!

*   ### 100% SSL Secure
    
    All of our forms are hosted on 256-bit SSL encrypted pages. Captcha integration makes sure all users are human.
    
*   ### Analytics & Reporting
    
    Out-of-the-box reports so you can find out how your forms are performing.
    
*   ### Customer Support
    
    Fast and friendly customer support to help you with all of your form needs.
    
*   ### Mobile
    
    View reports, access entries, and choose from hundreds of templates, all from your mobile device.
    
*   ### Form Template Gallery
    
    400+ ready-to-go form templates for quick form creation.
    
*   ### Theme Designer
    
    Easily customize the look and feel of your forms!
    
*   ### Field Validation
    
    Make sure your data comes in the way you want it.
    
*   ### Notifications
    
    Easily setup email and text message notifications.
    
*   ### Theme Gallery
    
    Start with any of our beautifully designed themes or build your own.
    
*   ### Custom Responses
    
    Quickly customize customer responses.
    
*   ### Social Sharing
    
    Easily share your forms to Facebook, Twitter, and more!
    
*   ### REST API
    
    Integrate your Wufoo data with your app!
    

Trusted by some of the world's leading brands
---------------------------------------------

![Image 1](https://www.wufoo.com/wp-content/themes/wufoo-site/img/client-strip-grayscale.png)

*   [### File Storage](https://www.wufoo.com/pricing/#)
    
    Storage is only allowed on paid accounts. It is used to hold files uploaded through the File Upload field. It is calculated across all forms on an account and the maximum size of file attachments that can be uploaded is 25MB.
    
*   [### FREE Account Limits](https://www.wufoo.com/pricing/#)
    
    On FREE accounts, forms will be deactivated once they have exceeded the maximum number of entries allowed for a given month.
    
*   [### Overages](https://www.wufoo.com/pricing/#)
    
    On PAID accounts, if you exceed the number of entries allowed for the month, a fee of $0.05 USD per entry over the limit will be charged to your account at the end of your billing period. All prices are $ USD unless otherwise noted.
    
*   [### Maximum Number of Fields](https://www.wufoo.com/pricing/#)
    
    Because checkboxes and text areas are handled differently on the database side in Wufoo, the maximum number of fields you can have on a form isn’t set in stone and is dependent on the type of data you’re collecting. Generally, this is about 100 fields, but it is limited by the number of checkbox (each choice counts as a field) and paragraph fields. Paragraph fields take up a lot more space on the database and so a maximum of 10 are allowed on a form.
    
*   [### Customer Support](https://www.wufoo.com/pricing/#)
    
    Customer support is handled via email. Our team is available Monday-Friday between 6AM and 5PM PST. Advanced and Ultimate customers are prioritized to receive responses as quickly as possible.
